00:14:12.440 --> 00:14:13.120
It's a bit cold.

00:14:13.120 --> 00:14:14.250
Just make do with it.

00:14:16.400 --> 00:14:17.880
You were right earlier.

00:14:18.720 --> 00:14:20.520
Everyone in the entertainment industry

00:14:20.520 --> 00:14:22.250
has their own survival skills.

00:14:23.200 --> 00:14:25.600
Those bouncers survive on connections.

00:14:26.480 --> 00:14:28.440
They don't even need to see their faces

00:14:28.440 --> 00:14:30.840
to recognize the bosses and cozy up to them.

00:14:32.280 --> 00:14:33.940
How many people are like that?

00:14:34.640 --> 00:14:37.120
The thing is, we can't check them one by one.

00:14:37.920 --> 00:14:39.520
The killer won't wait for us.

00:14:44.040 --> 00:14:45.370
I actually have an idea.

00:14:52.840 --> 00:14:53.320
Master.

00:14:53.400 --> 00:14:54.130
Brother Yan.

00:14:54.280 --> 00:14:55.840
I found out there was a crackdown last year.

00:14:55.840 --> 00:14:57.880
Hao Weiguo and his men hadn't worked for over three months,

00:14:57.880 --> 00:14:59.840
and they almost lost control of their underlings.

00:14:59.840 --> 00:15:00.640
But suddenly one day,

00:15:00.640 --> 00:15:02.280
Hao Weiguo received a phone call

00:15:02.280 --> 00:15:03.760
and went out alone with his wallet.

00:15:03.760 --> 00:15:04.920
When he came back,

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:06.240
he was carrying a bag of cash.

00:15:06.240 --> 00:15:08.440
I suspect this bag of cash is related to the film.

00:15:08.440 --> 00:15:09.370
Get to the point.

00:15:10.280 --> 00:15:11.240
Since it was in cash,

00:15:11.240 --> 00:15:12.040
it's hard to trace.

00:15:12.040 --> 00:15:13.880
We can only check call logs from the past six months.

00:15:13.880 --> 00:15:15.520
So we had to screen his contacts,

00:15:15.520 --> 00:15:16.480
one by one.

00:15:16.600 --> 00:15:18.960
But there are over 3,000 numbers in his contacts.

00:15:18.960 --> 00:15:19.560
What about the camera?

00:15:19.560 --> 00:15:20.490
Did you check it?

00:15:21.200 --> 00:15:23.800
We've asked all the photo labs and camera shops in town.

00:15:23.800 --> 00:15:25.920
As for this Minox camera and film,

00:15:25.920 --> 00:15:27.050
no one has sold them.

00:15:27.280 --> 00:15:28.480
But a boss said

00:15:28.480 --> 00:15:30.120
it might have been bought from a big city

00:15:30.120 --> 00:15:31.050
or by mail order.

00:15:31.760 --> 00:15:33.420
What about the closed stores?

00:15:33.480 --> 00:15:34.540
The closed stores.

00:15:37.920 --> 00:15:39.580
The photo is from before 2005.

00:15:39.680 --> 00:15:42.120
Since digital cameras and cell phones are developing so fast now,

00:15:42.120 --> 00:15:44.380
is it possible that the store has closed?

00:15:49.400 --> 00:15:49.880
Oh.

00:15:50.400 --> 00:15:51.000
Master, Brother Yan,

00:15:51.000 --> 00:15:52.440
how come you are so smart?

00:15:53.000 --> 00:15:54.330
I'll go check right now.

00:15:57.400 --> 00:15:58.720
Young people nowadays

00:15:59.000 --> 00:16:01.060
really can't compare to us back then.

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:04.320
Back then,

00:16:05.640 --> 00:16:06.520
you didn't seem much better than him.

00:16:06.520 --> 00:16:06.960
Stop.

00:16:07.200 --> 00:16:08.000
Stop right there.

00:16:08.000 --> 00:16:09.920
That's why people say you have no friends.

00:16:09.920 --> 00:16:10.400
Tsk.

00:16:11.040 --> 00:16:12.100
Hey, wait a minute.

00:16:17.200 --> 00:16:17.800
Tonight,

00:16:18.480 --> 00:16:20.610
I'll take you out to make some friends.

00:16:35.720 --> 00:16:36.280
Dr. Tong.

00:16:36.520 --> 00:16:37.760
Dr. Tong, I'm begging you.

00:16:37.760 --> 00:16:38.290
Dr. Tong.

00:16:38.360 --> 00:16:39.200
Please save us.

00:16:39.200 --> 00:16:39.730
Dr. Tong.

00:16:40.400 --> 00:16:41.240
Please save us.

00:16:41.240 --> 00:16:41.840
Please,

00:16:42.080 --> 00:16:43.080
help us.

00:16:43.120 --> 00:16:43.960
I'm begging you.

00:16:43.960 --> 00:16:44.600
Dr. Tong.

00:16:45.440 --> 00:16:46.000
Please!

00:16:46.000 --> 00:16:47.400
We've seen all the doctors we could.

00:16:47.400 --> 00:16:48.080
There's really nothing else we can do.

00:16:48.080 --> 00:16:48.680
Please help us.

00:16:48.680 --> 00:16:50.040
Get up. Get up first and listen to me.

00:16:50.040 --> 00:16:50.770
Get up first.

00:16:50.800 --> 00:16:51.520
Save us.

00:16:51.680 --> 00:16:52.160
Get up.

00:16:52.160 --> 00:16:53.040
Pull them up.

00:16:53.040 --> 00:16:53.680
Hurry.

00:16:54.040 --> 00:16:54.760
Get them up.

00:16:55.200 --> 00:16:56.120
Don't worry.

00:16:56.240 --> 00:16:57.200
What did you just say?

00:16:57.200 --> 00:16:57.920
What's the problem?

00:16:57.920 --> 00:16:59.120
My dad also has lung cancer.

00:16:59.120 --> 00:17:00.240
You must help us.

00:17:00.320 --> 00:17:01.200
Please save us.

00:17:01.720 --> 00:17:02.250
Dr. Tong.

00:17:02.280 --> 00:17:03.320
Please help them, Dr. Tong.

00:17:03.320 --> 00:17:04.560
Do you have the medical records?

00:17:04.560 --> 00:17:05.520
Yes, yes.

00:17:06.000 --> 00:17:07.079
Stage four.

00:17:07.440 --> 00:17:07.760
Yes.

00:17:07.760 --> 00:17:08.440
It's hard to treat.

00:17:08.440 --> 00:17:10.160
It's hard to treat at stage four.

00:17:10.160 --> 00:17:11.200
We will pay any price to treat him.

00:17:11.200 --> 00:17:11.730
Dr. Tong.

00:17:11.800 --> 00:17:13.200
My mother left this to me.

00:17:13.319 --> 00:17:14.040
Hey, no, no, no.

00:17:14.040 --> 00:17:15.000
Keep it.

00:17:15.079 --> 00:17:15.760
Put it away.

00:17:15.920 --> 00:17:16.800
You can't do this,

00:17:16.800 --> 00:17:17.359
you know?

00:17:18.240 --> 00:17:18.560
Alas.

00:17:18.560 --> 00:17:20.640
Filial children like you are rare nowadays,

00:17:20.640 --> 00:17:21.200
you know.

00:17:22.079 --> 00:17:22.760
Here's the thing.

00:17:22.760 --> 00:17:23.290
You guys,

00:17:23.359 --> 00:17:24.319
don't go to this hospital anymore.

00:17:24.319 --> 00:17:25.560
Don't bother registering under my name.

00:17:25.560 --> 00:17:26.599
Once you enter the hospital for this disease,

00:17:26.599 --> 00:17:28.530
the money will flow out like water.

00:17:28.920 --> 00:17:29.800
Here's what I'll do.

00:17:29.800 --> 00:17:31.120
I'll write you a prescription.

00:17:31.120 --> 00:17:33.050
Try it for one or two courses first.

00:17:33.280 --> 00:17:34.600
Go to the traditional Chinese medicine pharmacy across the street

00:17:34.600 --> 00:17:35.730
to get the medicine.

00:17:36.120 --> 00:17:37.440
If it works well,

00:17:37.800 --> 00:17:39.130
and it definitely will,

00:17:39.360 --> 00:17:40.200
come find me again.

00:17:40.200 --> 00:17:40.920
Thank you, Doctor.

00:17:40.920 --> 00:17:41.640
Oh, my.

00:17:41.640 --> 00:17:42.360
Thank you, Doctor.

00:17:42.360 --> 00:17:43.000
Oh.

00:17:43.240 --> 00:17:43.880
Get up.

00:17:43.880 --> 00:17:44.640
Oh, get up and listen to me.

00:17:44.640 --> 00:17:45.200
Get up.

00:17:45.560 --> 00:17:46.760
What are you doing?

00:17:46.800 --> 00:17:47.520
In front of everyone.

00:17:47.520 --> 00:17:48.240
We're saved.

00:17:48.240 --> 00:17:49.000
Okay, okay.

00:17:49.040 --> 00:17:49.520
It's fine.

00:17:49.520 --> 00:17:51.000
Go on.

00:17:51.160 --> 00:17:51.840
No need to thank me.

00:17:51.840 --> 00:17:52.200
Okay?

00:17:52.840 --> 00:17:54.000
Dr. Tong is such a good person.

00:17:54.000 --> 00:17:54.640
Yeah.

00:17:54.920 --> 00:17:56.160
Good deeds are rewarded.

00:17:56.160 --> 00:17:57.280
Look at you.

00:17:57.800 --> 00:17:59.800
You aren't even a doctor here, and you...

00:17:59.800 --> 00:18:00.880
Stop talking.

00:18:01.680 --> 00:18:02.240
Let's change places

00:18:02.240 --> 00:18:02.880
and keep at it.

00:18:02.880 --> 00:18:03.440
Let's go.